00:20:40.640 --> 00:20:42.308
do zitst mayn tokhter.

00:20:42.311 --> 00:20:44.550
geborn finf un fuftsikstn yor.

00:20:45.315 --> 00:20:47.199
kh'leb mit ir tsuzamen.

00:20:47.390 --> 00:20:49.241
mit ir, mit ir tokhter.

00:20:49.466 --> 00:20:50.861
un azoy lebn mir.

00:20:51.778 --> 00:20:53.758
di gantse tsayt ⟨iz⟩ gelebt der man

00:20:53.769 --> 00:20:55.639
hobn mir ale gelebt tsuzamen

00:20:55.659 --> 00:20:58.235
yetst shoyn finf vokhn vi der man iz geshtorbn.

00:20:58.629 --> 00:21:00.716
bin ikh geblibn mit di tokhter lebn.

00:21:11.842 --> 00:21:12.883
UNK

00:21:18.134 --> 00:21:19.836
VEZE I EFSHAR

00:21:26.338 --> 00:21:28.070
AT UNK MEDABERET ⟨AL ZE⟩?

00:21:28.380 --> 00:21:29.677
UNK

00:21:29.713 --> 00:21:34.939
ACHSHAV YESH SIPUR ACHER SHEABA NIFTAR, ⟨ACHSHAV HI BOCHA LAZE⟩, AVAL

00:21:36.142 --> 00:21:38.685
BEN ADAM, AVAR DEVAR KAZE, ZE KASHE.
